<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.183280>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Austrocarabodes hendriksi sp. nov. A—Dorsal view with magnifications of lamellar seta (le) and sensillus (ss). B—detail of notogastral seta (dm) and ornamentation on notogaster. C—Ventral view. Scale bar 100 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/183280/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.183287>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Map of South Africa showing the distribution of A. hendriksi (filled squares), A. vernoncrookensis (filled circles) and A. luciensis (filled triangles)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/183287/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

